{{Unreferenced|date=August 2011}} This is a '''list of flags used in the [[Shia Islam|Shia Muslims]]'''.
The Shia Muslims flags usually include the color [[green]] in them, which is a symbol of [[Islam]], also a symbol of purity, fertility and peace. Common colors in Shia Muslims flags are red, white and green; common symbols are [[Lion and Sun]] and the [[Shahada]].
